To further that, we're also looking at finalizing our branding. No name changes, nothing extreme just getting it to a point where it's even more professional with again the help of our friends at AMGI.
A 2D PFP that looks cool on Twitter is not the future. That's much of what NFTs are right now but we want to be ahead of the curve of what you can actually do with your IP and your artwork
